<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.4.9">
<l>kompiṉārpoḻil vāykuyiliṉaṅ kōvintaṉkuṇam pāṭucīr</l>
<l>cempoṉārmatiḷ cūḻceḻuṅkaḻa ṉiyuṭaittiruk kōṭṭiyūr</l>
<l>nampaṉainara ciṅkaṉainaviṉ ṟēttuvārkaḷaik kaṇṭakāl</l>
<l>empirāṉtaṉa ciṉṉaṅkaḷiva rivareṉṟācaikaḷ tīrvaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In Tirukkōṭṭiyūr with fertile fields surrounded</l>
<l rend="indent">by walls made of superior red gold,</l>
<l rend="indent">where cuckoo flocks in groves fill the branches</l>
<l rend="indent">singing of the qualities of Govinda,</l>
<l>if [I] see those who praise [Him], saying “Nampaṉ” “Narasiṃha”,</l>
<l rend="indent">thinking, “All of these people are signs of our Lord,”</l>
<l rend="indent">I will have ended [my] longings.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
